summary: Adds a save file of one of my characters.
descriptionHtml:
This adds lemon to the game, I used the console to gain a few levels [smithing, and a few others] so She is at lvl 33 [or 32 :O]

The use this save game, You\'\'ll need The Ashen race, Besides that, I don\'t use any face texture add-ons, or anything like that. The body is Type used is CBBE, but use what you might like! Some quests are started, maybe only a quest or 2 done in em.

Thanks to Bethesda For the game, and for The ashen race [The 2 authors for it]
